{"product_id":"bee-it-face-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing and anti-age prevention face cream, with a soft and light texture, easy to apply. It has professional efficacy with 100% natural origin active ingredients NaturOxygen® and Pentavitin® EcoCert, Cosmos and Natrue certified, which increase metabolism and skin turnover, making the skin nourished, radiant and even younger. Enriched with Sodium Hyaluronate, Shea butter, Vitamin E, propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply and massage with circular movements to regenerate the skin, releasing your emotions.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Cetearyl alcohol, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Cetearyl glucoside, Sorbitan olivate, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum [Fragrance], Butyrospermum parkii (Shea) butter, Glycerin, Cyamopsis tetragonoloba (guar) gum, Tocopheryl acetate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Citric acid, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Saccharide isomerate, Hydroxycitronellal, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Saccharomyces lysate, Disodium succinate, Sodium citrate, Glutamic acid, Glycine, Threonine, Valine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245337014599,"sku":null,"price":10.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-face-cream-50ml-9846172.png?v=1756636044","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/bee-it-face-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}